Chocolate Lava Cake

27 min
$8
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

glutendairyeggs

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Cuisine:

AmericanFrench

Course:

Description

Indulge in a rich, gooey chocolate dessert that oozes melted chocolate from the center.

Ingredients

  • dark chocolate: 6 oz
  • unsalted butter: 1/2 cup
  • powdered sugar: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2
  • egg yolks: 2
  • all-purpose flour: 1/2 cup
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • salt: a pinch
